title: Bad Girl, Good Girl
lyrics: You don’t know me, you don’t know me You don’t know me, you don’t know me So shut up boy, so shut up boy So shut up boy, so shut up, shut up Apeseon han madido motadeo ni Dwiye seon nae yaegil anjoke hae eoyiga eobseo. Hello, hello, hello, na gateun yeojan cheo eum euro-euro-euro Bon geogateun de wae nareul pandanani nae ga hokshi duryeo un geoni Geoteuron bad girl, sogeuron good girl Nareul ja raljido motamyeon seo nae geo moseupman bomyeonseo Hanshiman yeojaro boneun neoye Shiseoni nan neomuna ugyeo Chum chul ttaen bad girl, sarangeun good girl Chum chuneun nae moseubeul bolttae neun Nnokseul noko bogoseo neun Keunani songarak jil haneun geu wiseoni nan neomuna ugyeo Nal gam dan, halsu i neun namjal chajayo jin jja namjareul chajayo Mallo man, namjada uncheokal namja mal go Nal bu ran, haehaji aneul namjan eopnayo jashin gami neomchyeo seo Naega na ilsu ige jayuropge du go meolliseo bara bo neun Geoteuron bad girl, sogeuron good girl Nareul ja raljido motamyeon seo nae geo moseupman bomyeonseo Hanshiman yeojaro boneun neoye Shiseoni nan neomuna ugyeo Chum chul ttaen bad girl, sarangeun good girl Chum chuneun nae moseubeul bolttae neun Nnokseul noko bogoseo neun Keunani songarak jil haneun geu wiseoni nan neomuna ugyeo
